long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you tired of seeing unwanted AI search results cluttering your Google™ searches? YETI is here to enhance your browsing experience by letting you remove those distractions effortlessly. But that's not all—YETI also empowers you to apply your own custom CSS to any webpage, putting you in control of how the internet looks to you.
 
Features:

Remove Unwanted AI Search Results: Say goodbye to AI-generated clutter on Google™ search pages. YETI removes these elements so you can focus on the results that matter to you.

Custom CSS: Personalize your browsing experience by applying custom CSS to any webpage. Whether you want to hide elements, change colors, or adjust layouts, YETI makes it easy.

Simple and Intuitive: YETI is designed with ease of use in mind. A simple toggle lets you turn the extension on and off, and saving your custom CSS is just a click away.


Upcoming Features:

URL-Specific Custom CSS: Soon, you'll be able to apply different CSS rules to specific websites, giving you even more control over your browsing experience.


Why Choose YETI?

YETI is more than just a tool; it's a way to take charge of your online environment. By removing unnecessary AI search results and allowing for extensive customization, YETI makes browsing the web a more pleasant and productive experience. Whether you're a developer looking to test styles on the fly or a casual user wanting a cleaner search page, YETI has you covered.
